---
title: One-Pan Spicy Carolina BBQ Chicken Tacos with Creamy Slaw
description: Carolina BBQ is known for the spicy, mustard-spike sauce that tops slow-cooked, pulled meat. These tacos aren’t just about the BBQ though: you’ll add pickled jalapeño, crispy fried onion, and a creamy slaw. The best part? This taco night takes just 15-minutes to get to your plate, and only a few more seconds to get into your belly!
